Overcharged for my order. Then the cashier argued with me as to what I ordered. I know what I order. It&#39;s what I get whenever I stop for breakfast at McDonald&#39;s. I don&#39;t order the &#34;meal&#34;, yet that&#39;s what I was charged for and what the cashier claims I ordered. Even when he had asked me &#34;do you want the meal?&#34;, and I replied, &#34;no thank you.&#34;

Oh, and this location is more expensive than other Naperville locations. Must be because it&#39;s close to the interstate.

I&#39;ll never stop here again!
